# Checkwright gate registry — gate-sdk/SPEC.md §Layout and configuration.
# Names resolve against scripts/ first, then each vendored kit's checks/. The
# kits govern this repo too, day one: gate-sdk's meta-gates run on the
# kits themselves, and lifecycle-kit's stage gates run on this repo's own
# iteration state (TASK-QUEUE.md + .workflow/WORKFLOW-STATE.txt).
check-shellcheck
check-gate-output
check-gate-fail-closed
check-gate-fixture-coverage
check-gate-exemption-tasks
check-gate-assertions
check-graph
check-core-files
check-identity
check-stage-evidence
check-stage-entry
check-queue-hygiene
check-queue-wrap
check-tag-lead-line
check-task-names
check-task-conservation
check-queue-prose-precondition
check-amendment-queue
check-spec-dod-singleton
check-spec-derivable-section
check-spec-embedded-source
check-manifest-temporal
check-manifest-count
check-comment-tier
check-spec-pointer
check-gate-tamper
check-brevity
